{"id":372603,"name":null,"username":"Lawrence","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png","created_at":"2012-02-20T23:07:08.000Z","cooked":"<p>-sadface-<br>\nWell, I cant really say I didnt see that coming. But exactly what is the issue? I think clover boxes can be easily deleted and health increased even with very basic scene editing tools, no? So Id say the problem are actor scripts But even with the LBA2 Scene Manager (which, if I recall correctly is even outdated) you could watch and edit them, hasnt anyone figured out how the script commands work? Is that the problem?<br>\nSorry Im being so persistent, I just wanna understand the situation <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":4,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:52:12.672Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":13984,"topic_slug":"lba2-hard-mode-concept","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":3071,"username":"Lawrence","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"\\-sadface-\nWell, I can't really say I didn't see that coming. But exactly what is the issue? I think clover boxes can be easily deleted and health increased even with very basic scene editing tools, no? So I'd say the problem are actor scripts... But even with the LBA2 Scene Manager (which, if I recall correctly is even outdated) you could watch and edit them, hasn't anyone figured out how the script commands work? Is that the problem?\nSorry I'm being so persistent, I just wanna understand the situation :P","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":3071,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-hard-mode-concept/13984/4","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
