{"id":372686,"name":null,"username":"Zink","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/zink/{size}/61_2.png","created_at":"2012-02-23T08:16:08.000Z","cooked":"<p>Hmm, is that the reason? I thought the commands were known among developers. I have them, but its only a list of track and life commands/vars with their code values, no description or parameter info. If anyone wants - just ask me (not sure if Im allowed to make it available publicly).</p>","post_number":7,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:52:15.623Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":13984,"topic_slug":"lba2-hard-mode-concept","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":3071,"username":"Lawrence","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Hmm, is that the reason? I thought the commands were known among developers. I have them, but it's only a list of track and life commands/vars with their code values, no description or parameter info. If anyone wants - just ask me (not sure if I'm allowed to make it available publicly).","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":184,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-hard-mode-concept/13984/7","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_u