{"id":372688,"name":null,"username":"Lawrence","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png","created_at":"2012-02-23T08:36:46.000Z","cooked":"<p>Well, I have another problem now I cant edit those commands at all. LBA Scene Editor is horribly bugged, for example: I delete an actors life script and paste in a new one that is different, save the changes, check again the script and for some odd reason the original script is STILL there, except garbled up with a few characters from the script I pasted in (which makes the game crash)<br>\nIs there any tool that actually works that lets me edit actor scripts? <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/frowning_face.png?v=12\" title=\":frowning_face:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":frowning_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>","post_number":8,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:52:15.682Z","reply_count":1,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":5.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":13984,"topic_slug":"lba2-hard-mode-concept","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":3071,"username":"Lawrence","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Well, I have another problem now... I can't edit those commands at all. LBA Scene Editor is horribly bugged, for example: I delete an actor's life script and paste in a new one that is different, save the changes, check again the script and for some odd reason the original script is STILL there, except garbled up with a few characters from the script I pasted in (which makes the game crash)\nIs there any tool that actually works that lets me edit actor scripts? :(","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":3071,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-hard-mode-concept/13984/8","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":372877,"name":null,"username":"Battler","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/battler/{size}/208_2.png","created_at":"2012-02-29T14:22:12.000Z","cooked":"<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"Lawrence\" data-post=\"8\" data-topic=\"13984\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img loading=\"lazy\" alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"//forum.magicball.net/user_avatar/localhost/lawrence/48/607_2.png\" class=\"avatar\"> Lawrence:</div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Well, I have another problem now I cant edit those commands at all. LBA Scene Editor is horribly bugged, for example: I delete an actors life script and paste in a new one that is different, save the changes, check again the script and for some odd reason the original script is STILL there, except garbled up with a few characters from the script I pasted in (which makes the game crash)<br>\nIs there any tool that actually works that lets me edit actor scripts? <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/frowning_face.png?v=12\" title=\":frowning_face:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":frowning_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>Yes of course, the script part of the released version of the LBA Scene Manager is very buggy. Im working on an improvement (Ive also PMd Zink about the LBA 2 script commands) but I have no idea on how much its going to take.</p>","post_number":9,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T20:01:24.346Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":8,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":13984,"topic_slug":"lba2-hard-mode-concept","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"bookmarked":false,"raw":"\n[quote=\"Lawrence,post:8,topic:13984\"]\nWell, I have another problem now... I can't edit those commands at all. LBA Scene Editor is horribly bugged, for example: I delete an actor's life script and paste in a new one that is different, save the changes, check again the script and for some odd reason the original script is STILL there, except garbled up with a few characters from the script I pasted in (which makes the game crash)\nIs there any tool that actually works that lets me edit actor scripts? :(\n[/quote]\nYes of course, the script part of the released version of the LBA Scene Manager is very buggy. I'm working on an improvement (I've also PM'd Zink about the LBA 2 script commands) but I have no idea on how much it's going to take.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":1016,"hidden":false,"trust_level":2,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-hard-mode-concept/13984/9","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":372879,"name":null,"username":"Lawrence","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png","created_at":"2012-02-29T17:34:56.000Z","cooked":"<p>Well, thank you and anyone working on these programs for your efforts. <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"> I remain hopeful</p>","post_number":10,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T18:52:22.085Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":0,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":0.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":13984,"topic_slug":"lba2-hard-mode-concept","display_username":null,"primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":3071,"username":"Lawrence","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"Well, thank you and anyone working on these programs for your efforts. :) I remain hopeful","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":3071,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-hard-mode-concept/13984/10","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
{"id":373020,"name":"Jack McKalling","username":"Jack_McKalling","avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/jack_mckalling/{size}/624_2.png","created_at":"2012-03-04T22:06:26.000Z","cooked":"<p>If you still want to play hard mode in LBA2, you could consider one or more <a href=\"/t/lba-challenge-thread/13829/13\">challenges</a>?</p>\n<p>Its not hard coded features, but if youre truthful to yourself and consistent, these could be alot harder than normal playthrough. Also dont be afraid of using <a href=\"/t/lba1-2-glitchs-bugs/13891/1\">known bugs/glitches</a> <img src=\"//forum.magicball.net/plugins/discourse-lba-emoji/images/takam/stuck_out_tongue.png?v=12\" title=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" class=\"emoji emoji-custom\" alt=\":stuck_out_tongue:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p>\n<p>Youre not limited to only the proven ones or only the unconfirmed ones, just take any challenge you like, read the description and go ahead. We all (me specifically) would appreciate it if you were able to prove the possibility of one of the red ones, but you dont need to.</p>","post_number":11,"post_type":1,"posts_count":11,"updated_at":"2024-10-25T20:01:25.081Z","reply_count":0,"reply_to_post_number":1,"quote_count":0,"incoming_link_count":1,"reads":0,"readers_count":0,"score":5.0,"yours":false,"topic_id":13984,"topic_slug":"lba2-hard-mode-concept","display_username":"Jack McKalling","primary_group_name":null,"flair_name":null,"flair_url":null,"flair_bg_color":null,"flair_color":null,"flair_group_id":null,"badges_granted":[],"version":1,"can_edit":false,"can_delete":false,"can_recover":false,"can_see_hidden_post":false,"can_wiki":false,"user_title":null,"reply_to_user":{"id":3071,"username":"Lawrence","name":null,"avatar_template":"/user_avatar/forum.magicball.net/lawrence/{size}/607_2.png"},"bookmarked":false,"raw":"If you still want to play \"hard mode\" in LBA2, you could consider one or more [challenges](/t/lba-challenge-thread/13829/13)?\n\nIt's not hard coded features, but if you're truthful to yourself and consistent, these could be alot harder than normal playthrough. Also don't be afraid of using [known bugs/glitches](/t/lba1-2-glitchs-bugs/13891/1) :p\n\nYou're not limited to only the proven ones or only the unconfirmed ones, just take any challenge you like, read the description and go ahead. We all (me specifically) would appreciate it if you were able to prove the possibility of one of the \"red\" ones, but you don't need to.","actions_summary":[{"id":2,"can_act":true},{"id":6,"can_act":true},{"id":3,"can_act":true},{"id":4,"can_act":true},{"id":8,"can_act":true},{"id":10,"can_act":true},{"id":7,"can_act":true}],"moderator":false,"admin":false,"staff":false,"user_id":3189,"hidden":false,"trust_level":1,"deleted_at":null,"user_deleted":false,"edit_reason":null,"can_view_edit_history":false,"wiki":false,"post_url":"/t/lba2-hard-mode-concept/13984/11","reactions":[],"current_user_reaction":null,"reaction_users_count":0,"current_user_used_main_reaction":false,"can_accept_answer":false,"can_unaccept_answer":false,"accepted_answer":false,"topic_accepted_answer":null}
